ity\nthese instruments may detect these IMBH-SBH mergers in the coming years.\n\\textit{LISA} and the Einstein Telescope will be best suited to detect these GW\nevents. The inspirals of IMBH-SBH systems may also generate an unresolved GW\nbackground.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Nov 2017 18:00:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Feb 2018 07:28:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2018 13:10:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-11"}
