e discuss the patterns and clustering features of two-step SC\ntransitions, in which the AF-like phase is realized in the intermediate\ntemperature region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Nov 2017 08:10:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-03"}
