and damping timescale are $\\sim$52 Mm, $\\sim$50 km\ns$^{-1}$, $\\sim$99 minutes, and 2.5 hr, respectively. To our knowledge, this is\nthe first report of simultaneous transverse and longitudinal prominence\noscillations triggered by a coronal jet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Nov 2017 10:02:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
